{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":579,"text":"I would like to demonstrate\nfor the first time in public"},{"time":4048,"text":"that it is possible to transmit a video"},{"time":8143,"text":"from a standard off-the-shelf LED lamp"},{"time":12476,"text":"to a solar cell with a laptop\nacting as a receiver."},{"time":18478,"text":"There is no Wi-Fi involved,\nit's just light."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21093,"text":"And you may wonder, what's the point?"},{"time":23951,"text":"And the point is this:"},{"time":26399,"text":"There will be a massive\nextension of the Internet"},{"time":29099,"text":"to close the digital divide,"},{"time":31933,"text":"and also to allow for what we call\n\"The Internet of Things\" --"},{"time":36138,"text":"tens of billions of devices\nconnected to the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39328,"text":"In my view, such an extension\nof the Internet can only work"},{"time":43383,"text":"if it's almost energy-neutral."},{"time":46173,"text":"This means we need to use existing\ninfrastructure as much as possible."},{"time":51497,"text":"And this is where the solar cell\nand the LED come in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56959,"text":"I demonstrated for the first time,"},{"time":59301,"text":"at TED in 2011,"},{"time":61290,"text":"Li-Fi, or Light Fidelity."},{"time":63781,"text":"Li-Fi uses off-the-shelf LEDs\nto transmit data incredibly fast,"},{"time":69800,"text":"and also in a safe and secure manner."},{"time":73402,"text":"Data is transported by the light,"},{"time":76307,"text":"encoded in subtle changes\nof the brightness."},{"time":80390,"text":"If we look around,\nwe have many LEDs around us,"},{"time":83978,"text":"so there's a rich infrastructure\nof Li-Fi transmitters around us."},{"time":89393,"text":"But so far, we have been using\nspecial devices -- small photo detectors,"},{"time":94656,"text":"to receive the information\nencoded in the data."},{"time":98940,"text":"I wanted to find a way to also use\nexisting infrastructure"},{"time":102856,"text":"to receive data from our Li-Fi lights."},{"time":106426,"text":"And this is why I have been looking into\nsolar cells and solar panels."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111016,"text":"A solar cell absorbs light\nand converts it into electrical energy."},{"time":116549,"text":"This is why we can use a solar cell\nto charge our mobile phone."},{"time":121559,"text":"But now we need to remember"},{"time":122989,"text":"that the data is encoded in subtle changes\nof the brightness of the LED,"},{"time":129244,"text":"so if the incoming light fluctuates,"},{"time":132617,"text":"so does the energy harvested\nfrom the solar cell."},{"time":136579,"text":"This means we have\na principal mechanism in place"},{"time":140112,"text":"to receive information from the light\nand by the solar cell,"},{"time":146246,"text":"because the fluctuations\nof the energy harvested"},{"time":149045,"text":"correspond to the data transmitted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151934,"text":"Of course the question is:"},{"time":154084,"text":"can we receive very fast and subtle\nchanges of the brightness,"},{"time":158268,"text":"such as the ones transmitted\nby our LED lights?"},{"time":162641,"text":"And the answer to that is yes, we can."},{"time":166637,"text":"We have shown in the lab"},{"time":168440,"text":"that we can receive up to 50\nmegabytes per second"},{"time":171946,"text":"from a standard, off-the-shelf solar cell."},{"time":174921,"text":"And this is faster than most\nbroadband connections these days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179437,"text":"Now let me show you in practice."},{"time":185095,"text":"In this box is a standard,\noff-the-shelf LED lamp."},{"time":191193,"text":"This is a standard,\noff-the-shelf solar cell;"},{"time":193792,"text":"it is connected to the laptop."},{"time":196949,"text":"And also we have an instrument here"},{"time":199293,"text":"to visualize the energy\nwe harvest from the solar cell."},{"time":203095,"text":"And this instrument shows\nsomething at the moment."},{"time":205917,"text":"This is because the solar cell already\nharvests light from the ambient light."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211102,"text":"Now what I would like to do first\nis switch on the light,"},{"time":213966,"text":"and I'll simply, only switch on the light,"},{"time":216096,"text":"for a moment,"},{"time":218228,"text":"and what you'll notice is that\nthe instrument jumps to the right."},{"time":222904,"text":"So the solar cell, for a moment,"},{"time":224618,"text":"is harvesting energy\nfrom this artificial light source."},{"time":228540,"text":"If I turn it off, we see it drops."},{"time":231842,"text":"I turn it on ..."},{"time":233049,"text":"So we harvest energy with the solar cell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236586,"text":"But next I would like to activate\nthe streaming of the video."},{"time":243418,"text":"And I've done this\nby pressing this button."},{"time":245766,"text":"So now this LED lamp here\nis streaming a video"},{"time":250513,"text":"by changing the brightness of the LED\nin a very subtle way,"},{"time":254669,"text":"and in a way that you can't\nrecognize with your eye,"},{"time":257191,"text":"because the changes\nare too fast to recognize."},{"time":261384,"text":"But in order to prove the point,"},{"time":263807,"text":"I can block the light of the solar cell."},{"time":268087,"text":"So first you notice\nthe energy harvesting drops"},{"time":271334,"text":"and the video stops as well."},{"time":273050,"text":"If I remove the blockage,\nthe video will restart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277357,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":283610,"text":"And I can repeat that."},{"time":285967,"text":"So we stop the transmission of the video\nand energy harvesting stops as well."},{"time":291242,"text":"So that is to show that the solar cell\nacts as a receiver."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296079,"text":"But now imagine that this LED lamp\nis a street light, and there's fog."},{"time":302106,"text":"And so I want to simulate fog,"},{"time":304433,"text":"and that's why I brought\na handkerchief with me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":308656,"text":"And let me put the handkerchief\nover the solar cell."},{"time":313905,"text":"First you notice"},{"time":315557,"text":"the energy harvested drops, as expected,"},{"time":319778,"text":"but now the video still continues."},{"time":322769,"text":"This means, despite the blockage,"},{"time":325412,"text":"there's sufficient light coming through\nthe handkerchief to the solar cell,"},{"time":329317,"text":"so that the solar cell is able to decode\nand stream that information,"},{"time":334856,"text":"in this case, a high-definition video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339040,"text":"What's really important here is that\na solar cell has become a receiver"},{"time":344627,"text":"for high-speed wireless signals\nencoded in light,"},{"time":348466,"text":"while it maintains its primary function\nas an energy-harvesting device."},{"time":353872,"text":"That's why it is possible"},{"time":356315,"text":"to use existing solar cells\non the roof of a hut"},{"time":360196,"text":"to act as a broadband receiver"},{"time":362713,"text":"from a laser station on a close by hill,\nor indeed, lamp post."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367605,"text":"And It really doesn't matter\nwhere the beam hits the solar cell."},{"time":371647,"text":"And the same is true"},{"time":372849,"text":"for translucent solar cells\nintegrated into windows,"},{"time":376666,"text":"solar cells integrated\ninto street furniture,"},{"time":380222,"text":"or indeed, solar cells integrated\ninto these billions of devices"},{"time":384789,"text":"that will form the Internet of Things."},{"time":386889,"text":"Because simply,"},{"time":388071,"text":"we don't want to charge\nthese devices regularly,"},{"time":390586,"text":"or worse, replace the batteries\nevery few months."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394418,"text":"As I said to you,"},{"time":396172,"text":"this is the first time\nI've shown this in public."},{"time":398514,"text":"It's very much a lab demonstration,"},{"time":400593,"text":"a prototype."},{"time":402276,"text":"But my team and I are confident\nthat we can take this to market"},{"time":405594,"text":"within the next two to three years."},{"time":408251,"text":"And we hope we will be able to contribute\nto closing the digital divide,"},{"time":413568,"text":"and also contribute"},{"time":414790,"text":"to connecting all these billions\nof devices to the Internet."},{"time":418370,"text":"And all of this without causing"},{"time":419919,"text":"a massive explosion\nof energy consumption --"},{"time":422395,"text":"because of the solar cells,\nquite the opposite."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424641,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425818,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}